      <td width="" valign="top">
          <p align="left"><strong>The Right Reverend George L.R. Bruce</strong><br />
            Diocesan Bishop of Ontario<br />
          Anglican Church of Canada</p>
          <p>90 Johnson Street<br />
          Kingston, Ontario<br />
          K7L 1X7<br />
          Telephone: 613-544-4774<br />
          Fax: 613-547-3745<br />
